{"tid":834020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬爾代夫親中總統連任失敗！民眾上街狂賀","createTime":"2018-09-24T02:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T04:02:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9d1fda9374afed8ae79e53344bc7ed17c73f4d","tid":834020,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/102642_8ae6e3aab704dc4d3d252dccf05717b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F102642_8ae6e3aab704dc4d3d252dccf05717b6.png&h=ba4838dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬爾地夫舉行總統大選，親中的強人總統雅門（Abdulla Yameen）意外敗北，選舉委員會於今天（24日）早上公布，反對派聯合推出的候選人索里（Ibrahim Mohamed Solih）得票率為58.3％，民眾歡欣鼓舞上街慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報導，雅門總統在任期間掌握極大權力，幾乎所有的競爭對手都被判入獄或被迫流亡。今年2月，他宣布全國進入緊急狀態，暫停憲法實施，並命令部隊闖入最高法院，逮捕了法官和反對黨人士，以避免自己遭到彈劾。<br />\n<br />\n在總統大選開始前，警方甚至突襲搜查反對派馬爾地夫民主黨（MDP）的競選總部，聲稱掌握了非法活動的情資，但最後沒有人被捕。外界更一度傳言雅門將不惜一切代價尋求連任保持權力。<br />\n<br />\n人權觀察組織表示，雅門政府使用了模糊不清的法律來鎮壓異議並恐嚇、監禁批評者，其中一些人遭到毆打甚至謀殺。<br />\n<br />\n馬爾地夫民主黨領導人納希德（Mohamed Nasheed），曾在2008年當選總統，卻被迫流亡在外，他強調雅門別無選擇，到了這個地步只能承認失敗。<br />\n<br />\n印度和中國都密切關注馬爾地夫總統大選，印度過去在馬爾地夫具有長期的影響力，他們早在1988年就派出軍隊與軍艦前往馬爾地夫，阻止政變發生。不過，雅門總統近年來相當親中，並從中國獲得數億美元的基礎建設資金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2560187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2560187&d=9V0snLNjGsSXGZAvKmetom6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c91e1261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2560187&h=db786203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2560187</a>"},{"pid":"2d4d7bee7e3f118f1fba2f8bc3c433384592d77d","tid":834020,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0bcc5c8a12eccd7e1f2257cb76bac408990821","tid":834020,"uid":69213,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46186dc6e13fae25f567d7c9ab88421ad18d26c9","tid":834020,"uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/R0kCLG2sfeCwE/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FR0kCLG2sfeCwE%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=248beb79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3a7f8be4b23f902f4cb204ea6461c0c01170534","tid":834020,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"支那又贏"},{"pid":"378475ffbe0843df01a587a8b2ede0dbf7dcf4c0","tid":834020,"uid":44454,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"咁啲欠債咪變成歷史文件囉"},{"pid":"0ee5a11b99ba1fc924c483af06a6d8f90aec195d","tid":834020,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"無左個港口既係唔係呢個國家?"},{"pid":"cdd6f4d9cced7235d52feb4f51f84bfbef5a9e6e","tid":834020,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"631db40d42f403d9f7a70fc1e4acfbd650e68cec","tid":834020,"uid":67331,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0ee5a11b99ba1fc924c483af06a6d8f90aec195d","tid":834020,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"無左個港口既係唔係呢個國家?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"斯里蘭卡，好似係"},{"pid":"a58fd544f95ab5ff9ed161ce1240be56f9da2d5d","tid":834020,"uid":45376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n贏國一人一啖口水都搞到佢陸沉啦"},{"pid":"b6fde4a27083ed43bc12d2c8004335cafe254282","tid":834020,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislik